  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Difficult combat,</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >for those who crave the relief of overcoming difficult challenges: <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801670/extras/d436cd809a56a4bd7e363b0caab767a0.poster.avif?t=1743765535\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801670/extras/d436cd809a56a4bd7e363b0caab767a0.webm?t=1743765535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801670/extras/d436cd809a56a4bd7e363b0caab767a0.mp4?t=1743765535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Boss Battles,</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With their own challenges and lore:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801670/extras/7d228f52c0cfe4ca6de42e0244190303.poster.avif?t=1743765535\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801670/extras/7d228f52c0cfe4ca6de42e0244190303.webm?t=1743765535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801670/extras/7d228f52c0cfe4ca6de42e0244190303.mp4?t=1743765535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Movement:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >use the provided movement to maintain a consistent distance to your enemies and to make pushes and escapes:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801670/extras/92479f2d335c2738655dfbc6e73ffce7.poster.avif?t=1743765535\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801670/extras/92479f2d335c2738655dfbc6e73ffce7.webm?t=1743765535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801670/extras/92479f2d335c2738655dfbc6e73ffce7.mp4?t=1743765535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This game also features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of collectable perks such as: seeing enemies through walls, slowing time, and autofiring</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple gamemodes such as: the floor is lava, no healing, and weapon shuffle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of weapons, such as bows, shotguns, and SMGs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of enemies such as: machine gunners, riot shielders, and shotgunners</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sandbox-like difficulty options such as: changing enemy behaviour, player damage, and removal of heal limitations</p></li></ul>",
